This paper is about flow-based generative models for image synthesis with conditional information. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision), which focuses on image and video processing. The second likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers various topics related to machine learning, including generative models. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), which includes papers on various aspects of AI, including image synthesis. The fourth likely category is cs.GR (Graphics), which covers topics related to computer graphics, including image synthesis. The fifth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which includes papers on various aspects of multimedia, including image and video processing.
